replies.body:
Admittedly, I'm super excited for the universe DJ Sona gets to be in.  Part of me wishes it could linked to Pentakill because a member of a band going solo is SO cool to me, but that wouldn't make any sense in-universe.  Popstar Ahri would be cool, though.  It'd be so cool having some kind of music festival, convention or something.  I'm a musician myself, so I have a soft spot for those skins (especially Sona!).

I would've expected Statue of Karthus to be one of those that was passed up entirely, haha.  I know skin lines are popular, but I normally prefer ones that are "unique" in that they're not linked to anything else.  It feels like something specially made for the champ.  Divine Soraka, Bladecraft Orianna, Tempest Janna, Elementalist Lux (actually my favorite; I could write a dissertation).  Part of me wants to stay on my island, but regardless I'm looking forward to it.

{{sticker:sg-lulu}}
